author: Matt Stout
title: Karyn Polito’s furious fundraising pace
text:
Lt. Gov. Karyn Polito is on a fundraising pace unmatched by her recent predecessors in state government’s little-known and much mocked second-ban-ana role, pulling in nearly $900,000 for her and Gov. Charlie Baker’s already impressive war chest.
